# LookAroundErrorEvent

**Type**

A custom event object that contains information about the error when starting a Look Around view.

## Declaration

```swift
type LookAroundErrorEvent = CustomEvent<{
    type: LookAroundErrorType;
    message: string;
}>;
```

## Discussion

The event object describes the error with a [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/LookAroundErrorType] value and a message.

## Events and event properties

- **LookAroundErrorType**: Values that describes errors than can occur when starting a Look Around view.
